I have access to a code repository in the directory /workspace/oxc/ . You can explore and modify files using the available tools. Consider the following issue description:

<issue_description>
formatter: Diff with Prettier on single-line comments in an empty enum
### Input

```tsx
type Foo = {
  // Type comment
};

interface Bar {
  // Interface comment
}

enum Baz {
  // Enum comment, this will break after formatting
}

```

### Config

```jsonc
{}
```

### Oxfmt output

Oxfmt version: `latest`
```tsx
type Foo = {
  // Type comment
};

interface Bar {
  // Interface comment
}

enum Baz {// Enum comment, this will break after formatting}

```

